    <div class="card">
      <h2>Research Interests</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Statistical learning under complex data conditions: semi-supervised learning, informative missingness, mixture models, robust estimation.</li>
        <li>Computational statistics and optimisation: high-dimensional and non-convex optimisation, stochastic and iterative algorithms, swarm-based methods.</li>
        <li>Time-series and forecasting: probabilistic forecasting in energy, environmental, and socio-economic systems; causal mechanisms in dynamical systems.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h2>Selected Topics</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Support vector regression with automatic hyperparameter selection and heterogeneous variances.</li>
        <li>Semi-supervised learning in finite mixture models with mixed missingness mechanisms.</li>
        <li>Robust regression and deep learning models for power load and environmental forecasting.</li>
      </ul>
